`python -c 'import onnx; print(onnx.helper.make_tensor_value_info("Z", onnx.TensorProto.FLOAT, ()))'`

before:
```
name: "Z"
type {
  tensor_type {
    elem_type: FLOAT
  }
}
```

after:
```
name: "Z"
type {
  tensor_type {
    elem_type: FLOAT
    shape {
    }
  }
}
```
